1.  Concurrency kya hota hai?
    Multiple processes/threads ek hi time period mein exist karte hain aur potentially interact karte hain. Yeh actually parallel nahi
    bhi ho sakta — single CPU pe time-sharing se bhi concurrency hoti hai. Concurrency se race conditions aur deadlocks jaisi problems
    aati hain.
    Interview Tip: Concurrency ≠ Parallelism: Concurrency = multiple tasks manage karo. Parallel = actually ek saath run.

